{"tid":561583,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到其他嘅分手post我就覺得好鼓舞","createTime":"2018-02-15T06:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T11:25:56.000Z","uid":169676,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67a04fc113f7092557de5756c0ca31e4e68a1b50","tid":561583,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:36:53.000Z","msg":"分手原來可以咁易架<br />\n一齊咗幾耐都好<br />\n投資咗幾多感情係入面都好<br />\n一句話唔適合<br />\n就可以即時分手<br />\n易過cut有線<br />\n真係好興奮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsorry<br />\n我唔係幸災樂禍<br />\n我只係覺得<br />\n如果我心愛嘅女仔<br />\n同佢另一半分咗手<br />\n咁就真係太美好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係未好變態好唔常呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdffe44aa65352270062b6c95f29e6b95f33c614","tid":561583,"uid":169676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:45:18.000Z","msg":"唉呢種諗法真係好唔德道<br />\n會有報應架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係內心深處又好希望真係會咁<br />\n如果係真<br />\n我諗我會好似呢隻腦魔咁陰陰嘴笑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後到個陣我就會再次充滿能量<br />\n每一日都會過得非常快樂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc17ac3f3176761a117aadf1f53484d54db50ca1","tid":561583,"uid":165482,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"就算條女分咗手都唔會揀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 